meta.title: Aimeos Distribution Package 2020.10
meta.description: Export settings for creating the Aimeos 2020.10 Distribution package.

rec.title: Aimeos Shop - Catalog User Related Sessi...
Aimeos Shop - Catalog User Related Sessi...

fieldlist.field:
page.theme.copyright.enable = 0 page.theme.breadcrumb = 0
page.logo.file = fileadmin/aimeos_dist/logo.png page.logo.height = 30px page.logo.width >
page.fluidtemplate.partialRootPath = EXT:aimeos_dist/Resources/Private/Partials/Page/
plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.brand-primary = #B0A060 plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.navbar-height = 20px plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.navbar-default-color = #B0A060 plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.navbar-default-link-color = lighten(@navbar-default-link-active-color,15%) plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.navbar-default-link-active-color = #B0A060 plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.btn-default-color = #B0A060 plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.btn-font-weight = bold plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.grid-gutter-width = 20px plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.container-tablet = (730px + @grid-gutter-width) plugin.bootstrap_package.settings.less.container-tablet = (740px + @grid-gutter-width)

page.shortcutIcon = fileadmin/aimeos_dist/favicon.png
# Remove smoothscroll code in boostrap_package so changing images in detail view works page.includeJSFooterlibs.bootstrap_smoothscroll >
# From aimeos_dist/Configuration/TypoScript/constants.txt config.typolinkLinkAccessRestrictedPages = {$tx_aimeos.profile.target} config.typolinkLinkAccessRestrictedPages_addParams = &return_url=###RETURN_URL###
plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.basket.standard.url.target = {$tx_aimeos.basket.target} plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.mshop.customer.manager.typo3.pid-default = {$tx_aimeos.customer.pid}
# Aimeos debug log level #plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.madmin.log.manager.standard.loglevel = 7
# Disable basket caching for development # plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.basket.cache.enable = 0
# Default group IDs for newly created users (single value or array) plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.controller.frontend.customer.groupids = 3
# Show "add to basket" in list views #plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.lists.domains { # 0 = attribute # 1 = media # 2 = price # 3 = product # 4 = text #} #plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.lists.basket-add = 1
# Use alternative image partial for detail pages # plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.detail.partials.image = catalog/detail/image-partial-bottom.php
plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.selection.type.color = radio plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.selection.type.length = radio plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.selection.type.width = radio
plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.client.html.catalog.attribute.type.sticker = input
# Example for overwriting translations plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.i18n.de { 0 { domain = client/code string = sticker trans = Sticker } 1 { domain = client/code string = print trans = Aufdruck } } plugin.tx_aimeos.settings.i18n.en { 0 { domain = client string = Attributes trans = Filter } 1 { domain = client string = %1$d article trans { 0 = %1$d 1 = %1$d } } }
# Show small basket in the header # Add this to the main navigation Fluid template # <f:if condition="{f:cObject(typoscriptObjectPath:'lib.navigation.misc.basket')}"> # <f:cObject typoscriptObjectPath="lib.navigation.misc.basket" /> # </f:if>
lib.navigation.misc = COA lib.navigation.misc.basket = USER lib.navigation.misc.basket { userFunc = TYPO3\CMS\Extbase\Core\Bootstrap->run vendorName = Aimeos extensionName = Aimeos pluginName = basket-small controller = Basket action = small settings =< plugin.tx_aimeos.settings }
